Create a Naming and Profile Document
====================================

A *Naming and Profile Document* describes the certificates issued by AD CS. Such a document can be generated from the certificate templates stored in AD.

#. Log in to one of the domain controllers.

#. Export the certificate templates as LDIF-files using PowerShell::

{% for template in templates %}
    ldifde -m -v -d "CN={{ template.name.replace(' ', '') }},CN=Certificate Templates,CN=Public Key Services,CN=Services,CN=Configuration,DC={{ customer.domain.split('.')[0] }},DC={{ customer.domain.split('.')[1] }}" -f {{ template.name.replace(' ', '') }}.ldf
{% endfor %}

